  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为唱片店设计一个数据库模型。核心流程是销售记录，每次销售要关联到具体的唱片。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那销售记录Ventas这边需要存什么信息？客户信息是简单记录姓名，还是需要单独建表？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "nombreCliente",
        "apellidoCliente"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "客户信息直接存在销售表里就行，记录nombreCliente和apellidoCliente，不需要单独表。但每张唱片要关联到风格、演唱者和唱片公司。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos",
        "Generos",
        "Interprete",
        "Sello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把销售表建起来，包含numeroFactura作为主键，还有fechaVenta、nombreCliente、apellidoCliente，以及disco外键和cantidad。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "numeroFactura",
        "fechaVenta",
        "nombreCliente",
        "apellidoCliente",
        "disco",
        "cantidad"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，销售表这样没问题。唱片表Discos需要codigo做主键，记录fechaCreacion、nombre，还有precio。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discos",
        "codigo",
        "fechaCreacion",
        "nombre",
        "precio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "风格、演唱者和唱片公司我都做成独立实体吧，分别叫Generos、Interprete和Sello，这样唱片表通过外键关联过去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Generos",
        "Interprete",
        "Sello",
        "Discos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "可以，但Interprete这个表名用单数还是复数？我们习惯用单数表示实体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Interprete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修正了，用Interprete单数形式。现在检查关系：销售到唱片是多对一，唱片到风格、演唱者、唱片公司都是多对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos",
        "Generos",
        "Interprete",
        "Sello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，销售到唱片的关系画反了。一个销售记录只对应一张唱片，但一张唱片可以出现在多个销售记录里，所以是Ventas多对一Discos。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Ventas是零或多，Discos是一，关系标注为\"tiene\"。现在补充各表字段细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ventas",
        "Discos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Generos加descripcion字段，Interprete需要fechaNacimiento、nombre、apellido，Sello要email和domicilio。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Generos",
        "descripcion",
        "Interprete",
        "fechaNacimiento",
        "nombre",
        "apellido",
        "Sello",
        "email",
        "domicilio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部完成。最终确认：五个实体，Ventas零或多对一Discos，Discos多对一关联Generos、Interprete、Sello，所有主键外键关系正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
